data.eml:eml: SPC CoFish Invertebrates Observations Federated States of Micronesia 2006

Marine invertebrate species of commercial interest observed in Federated States of Micronesia during the CoFish surveys in Romanum, Piis-Panewu, Riiken and Yyin (2006) with a mix of survey methods (manta tow, reef benthos transects, and day and night searches)
